Package edu.ncsu.csc216.packdoption.util

Class Date

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.packdoption.util.Date
  • public class Date
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class Date is responsible for everything related to time keeping and checking if the date is a valid date. It has year, month, and day. Will have to have a clever way of checking the time between two dates due to changes in the number of days per month and other factors.
    Author:
    Cameron Dutra, Ian Fright
